&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="long_text"&gt;&lt;span title="If we want to preserve our digital heritage we all need to select  Open Standards, implementable by anyone, as our default storage  choice.” — Jeremy Allison, Samba core developer" style="background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;* fonte: &lt;a href="http://www.documentfreedom.org"&gt;DFD&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Mar 2010 16:42:27 +0000</pubDate><link>http://softwarelivre.org/furusho/blog/jeremy-allison-desenvolvedor-do-nucleo-do-samba-fala-sobre-o-dfd</link><guid>http://softwarelivre.org/furusho/blog/jeremy-allison-desenvolvedor-do-nucleo-do-samba-fala-sobre-o-dfd</guid></item><item><title>Simon Phipps apoia o Document Freedom Day - 31 março</title><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=""&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.webmink.com/about/"&gt;&lt;img class="avatar avatar-128" src="http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/356daffa0cecdbccc9d1b4449a92beb5?s=128&amp;amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F1.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D128&amp;amp;r=PG" height="128" alt="" width="128"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="long_text"&gt;&lt;span title="True open standards are the key to deployer  liberty." style="background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;Verdadeiros padrões abertos são a chave para a liberdade  implementador. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span title="'Libre' implementations of open standards - evolved in the  open with every willing voice respected - are already at the heart of  the new digital society and Document Freedom Day is to be welcomed as a  celebration of the liberties we all need for our networked future." style="background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;'Implementações  Livres' de padrões abertos - desenvolvido a céu aberto com todas as  vozes dispostas respeitado - já estão no cerne da nova sociedade digital  Document Freedom Day e deve ser saudada como uma celebração das  liberdades que todos nós precisamos para o nosso futuro em rede.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span title="” — Simon Phipps,  Free Software developer" style="background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="long_text"&gt;&lt;span title="” — Simon Phipps,  Free Software developer" style="background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;- Simon Phipps, desenvolvedor de Software  Livre&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="long_text"&gt;&lt;span title="” — Simon Phipps,  Free Software developer" style="background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;* fonte: www.DocumentoFreedomday.org&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Mar 2010 16:55:59 +0000</pubDate><link>http://softwarelivre.org/furusho/blog/simon-phipps-apoia-o-document-freedom-day-31-marco</link><guid>http://softwarelivre.org/furusho/blog/simon-phipps-apoia-o-document-freedom-day-31-marco</guid></item><item><title>Chris DiBona - Google, apóia padrões abertos.</title><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="http://www.documentfreedom.org/images/thumb/4/40/Chrisdibona.png/80px-Chrisdibona.png" alt="http://www.documentfreedom.org/images/thumb/4/40/Chrisdibona.png/80px-Chrisdibona.png"&gt; &lt;span class="long_text"&gt;&lt;span title="“Over time, files that have been saved in  closed formats tend to be less and less accessible to thier creators." style="background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;"Com  o tempo, os arquivos que foram salvos em formatos fechados tendem a ser  cada vez menos acessível para os seus criadores. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span title="We prefer people to  use modern and truly open formats like ODF whenever possible to ensure  that they can continue to access and enjoy their work today and into the  far future.” — Chris DiBona, Open Source Manager, Google" style="background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;Nós  preferimos utilizar moderno e verdadeiramente formatos  abertos como o ODF, sempre que possível para garantir que eles possam  continuar a acessar e desfrutar de seu trabalho hoje e no futuro  distante. "- Chris DiBona, Open Source, Google&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
